@page "/PrivacyPolicy"
@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy | Rencher Design";
}

<!-- Page Hero -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low border-b border-outline-variant/20">
  <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <span class="font-label text-secondary tracking-widest text-xs font-bold uppercase block mb-4">Privacy Policy</span>
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-headline leading-tight mb-6">Your information stays private.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant font-body font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Designing a home is an intensely personal process. You'll share details about your land, your family, your finances, and your vision for the life you want to live. That information is treated with the same care I bring to every drawing I produce.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Commitment — Featured -->
<section class="py-16 bg-primary text-white">
  <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-2xl font-serif italic text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
        "I don't share your private information with anyone. I retain only what's needed to do our work together."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Policy Sections -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface">
  <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">

      <!-- Sticky sidebar nav -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 hidden lg:block">
        <div class="sticky top-28 space-y-2">
          <p class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant mb-4">On This Page</p>
          <a href="#what-i-collect" class="block text-sm font-body text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors py-1">What I collect</a>
          <a href="#what-i-dont-do" class="block text-sm font-body text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors py-1">What I don't do</a>
          <a href="#how-long" class="block text-sm font-body text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors py-1">How long I keep it</a>
          <a href="#your-rights" class="block text-sm font-body text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors py-1">Your rights</a>
          <a href="#website" class="block text-sm font-body text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors py-1">This website</a>
          <a href="#contact-privacy" class="block text-sm font-body text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors py-1">Questions</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9 space-y-16">

        <!-- What I collect -->
        <div id="what-i-collect" class="scroll-mt-28">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mt-1">person</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline leading-snug">What I collect</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-body leading-relaxed font-light pl-12">
            <p>When you reach out through this website, I collect the information you choose to share — your name, contact details, and whatever you tell me about your project. As our engagement develops, that may grow to include details about your land, your household, your budget, and your design preferences.</p>
            <p>I collect only what's necessary to do good work for you. I don't ask for information I don't need, and I don't gather data in the background about how you browse or behave online beyond basic website analytics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What I don't do -->
        <div id="what-i-dont-do" class="scroll-mt-28">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mt-1">block</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline leading-snug">What I don't do</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-body leading-relaxed font-light pl-12">
            <p>I don't sell your information. I don't share it with advertisers, data brokers, or third-party marketing platforms. I don't use it to target you with advertising. I don't share it with other clients or prospective clients.</p>
            <p>The only people who may have access to your information are those directly involved in delivering your project — and only to the extent necessary. If your project requires me to coordinate with another professional or a government planning office, I share only what that specific conversation requires.</p>
            <p>I don't share your story with anyone else without your explicit permission. The details of what you're building and why you're building it are yours.</p>
          </div>
          <br>

        <!-- How long I keep it -->
        <div id="how-long" class="scroll-mt-28">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mt-1">schedule</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline leading-snug">How long I keep it</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-body leading-relaxed font-light pl-12">
            <p>I retain project records — drawings, correspondence, calculation notes — for as long as is reasonably necessary given the nature of home design. A home is a long-lived thing, and questions sometimes arise years after a project is complete. Keeping records allows me to support you if they do.</p>
            <p>If your inquiry doesn't result in a project, I don't hold onto your information beyond what's needed for a reasonable follow-up period. If you'd like me to delete what I have on file for you, just ask.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>

        <!-- Your rights -->
        <div id="your-rights" class="scroll-mt-28">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mt-1">verified_user</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline leading-snug">Your rights</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-body leading-relaxed font-light pl-12">
            <p>You have the right to know what information I hold about you, to request a copy of it, to ask me to correct anything that's wrong, and to ask me to delete it. None of those requests require justification. Just reach out.</p>
            <p>You also have the right to opt out of any communications from me at any time. If I've followed up with you about a project and you'd prefer not to hear from me, say so and I'll respect that immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>

        <!-- This website -->
        <div id="website" class="scroll-mt-28">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mt-1">language</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline leading-snug">This website</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-body leading-relaxed font-light pl-12">
            <p>This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect basic server logs — IP addresses, browser type, pages visited — as part of normal web infrastructure operation. That data is governed by Cloudflare's own privacy policy, which I encourage you to review if it matters to you.</p>
            <p>I may use a simple, privacy-respecting analytics tool to understand how many people visit the site and which pages they read. I don't use Google Analytics or any advertising-based tracking platform. I'm not interested in tracking you — I'm interested in designing homes.</p>
            <p>This site does not use cookies for advertising or cross-site tracking purposes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>

        <!-- Questions -->
        <div id="contact-privacy" class="scroll-mt-28">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mt-1">mail</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline leading-snug">Questions</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-body leading-relaxed font-light pl-12">
            <p>If you have any questions about this policy or about how I handle your information, reach out directly. There's no privacy team or ticketing system — it's just me.</p>
            <div class="mt-6 space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">mail</span>
                <a href="mailto:tyler@rencherdesign.com" class="font-body text-secondary hover:underline">tyler@rencherdesign.com</a>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">call</span>
                <span class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">435-562-5964</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>